## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="3aaba-179">경우는 <xref:System.Data.ParameterDirection> 출력과 연결 된 실행은 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> 값을 반환 하지 않습니다는 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> null 값을 포함 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3aaba-179">If the <xref:System.Data.ParameterDirection> is output, and execution of the associated <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> does not return a value, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> contains a null value.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3aaba-180">`Output`를 `InputOut`, 및 `ReturnValue` 호출에서 반환 하는 매개 변수 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand.ExecuteReader%2A> 호출할 때까지 액세스할 수 없습니다 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.Close%2A> 에 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3aaba-180">`Output`, `InputOut`, and `ReturnValue` parameters returned by calling <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand.ExecuteReader%2A> cannot be accessed until you call <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.Close%2A> on the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="3aaba-181">다음 예제에서는 한 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> 속성 중 일부를 설정 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3aaba-181">The following example creates a <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> and sets some of its properties.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Public Sub CreateOracleDbParameter()  
   Dim parameter As New OracleParameter()  
   parameter.ParameterName = "pDName"  
   parameter.DbType = DbType.String  
   parameter.Value = "ENGINEERING"  
   parameter.SourceColumn = "DName"  
End Sub  
```  
  
```csharp  
public void CreateOracleDbParameter()   
{  
   OracleParameter parameter = new OracleParameter();  
   parameter.ParameterName = "pDName";  
   parameter.DbType = DbType.String;  
   parameter.Value = "ENGINEERING";  
   parameter.SourceColumn = "DName";  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
