## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="3aaba-268">이 속성은 사용 합니다 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.UpdateCommand%2A> 중는 <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Update%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 원래 또는 현재 값을 매개 변수 값을 사용할지 여부를 확인 하려면.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3aaba-268">This property is used by the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.UpdateCommand%2A> during the <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Update%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> to determine whether the original or current value is used for a parameter value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3aaba-269">이렇게 하면 기본 키를 업데이트할 수 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3aaba-269">This lets primary keys be updated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3aaba-270">버전에이 속성은 <xref:System.Data.DataRow> 에서 사용 하는 합니다 <xref:System.Data.DataRow.Item%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 속성 (<xref:System.Data.DataRow> 인덱서), 또는 <xref:System.Data.DataRow.GetChildRows%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 메서드의 <xref:System.Data.DataRow> 개체.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3aaba-270">This property is set to the version of the <xref:System.Data.DataRow> used by the <xref:System.Data.DataRow.Item%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property (<xref:System.Data.DataRow> indexer), or the <xref:System.Data.DataRow.GetChildRows%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method of the <xref:System.Data.DataRow> object.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="3aaba-271">다음 예제에서는 한 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> 속성 중 일부를 설정 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3aaba-271">The following example creates a <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> and sets some of its properties.</span></span>  
  
